## PART VIII: EXPERIMENTAL PREDICTIONS

### VIII.1 The 93-Element Limit

The 93-node matrix predicts that atoms beyond atomic number 93 (neptunium) will have increasingly unstable electron configurations. This matches the observed instability of transuranic elements.

**The atom is Geofont. Geofont is the atom.**

